name: UNiagaraDataInterfaceSimCacheReader
doc: Data interface to read properties from a Niagara Simulation Cache

SimCacheBinding: User parameter Object binding if this is not a valid sim cache the default one will be used instead.
SimCache: Optional source SimCache to use, if the user parameter binding is valid this will be ignored.
EmitterBinding: Which Emitter we should read from within the SimCache.
